# Deploy & Hosting

- Live URL: https://geminus.surge.sh/
- Repo: https://github.com/betexcr/geminus-ratio.git (branch: main)
- Hosting: Surge.sh (account: albmunmu@gmail.com, Student plan)
- No build step — static HTML/CSS/JS served directly

## Git push

This repo uses the **betexcr** GitHub account. Before pushing, ensure it is the active `gh` account:

```bash
gh auth switch --user betexcr
git push origin main
```

## Deploy command

```bash
surge . geminus.surge.sh
```

## Local dev server

```bash
python3 -m http.server 8765
```

## Script load order (dependency chain)

rng.js -> sfx.js -> renderer.js -> sprites.js -> campaign.js -> game.js

## Persistence

Campaign saves use localStorage key `geminus_campaign_v2`.
